### Welcome to the SFX Player GitHub Page.
Here you will find the most up-to-date information about SFX Player and it's releases. Please remember this is a work-in-progress and until stated otherwise there is not an official release.

```
$ cd your_repo_root/repo_name
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```

If you're using the GitHub for Mac, simply sync your repository and you'll see the new branch.
